The paper deals with the design of frame-based transmissions in cellular wireless systems, which is a topic that falls under the intersection of information theory (cs.IT), networking and internet architecture (cs.NI), and systems and control (cs.SY). The paper also mentions the importance of short data packets in 5G and Internet of Things applications, which could potentially fall under multimedia (cs.MM) or machine learning (cs.LG) categories.
